    <summary><span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-101"><see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter" /> コントロールが領域を行間または列間のどちらで再配分するかを指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-101">Specifies whether a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter" /> control redistributes space between rows or between columns.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks

<span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-102">この列挙体を使用して、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> プロパティを設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-102">Use this enumeration to set the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>

## Remarks  

<span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-103">`Auto` 列挙値が <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> コントロールの領域の再配布に与える影響は、次のプロパティ値によって異なります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-103">How the `Auto` enumeration value affects the redistribution of space in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> control depends on the following property values:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-104"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されていない場合、列間で領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-104">If the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is not set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between columns.</span></span>  
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-105"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType> に設定されていて、<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> プロパティが <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>に設定されていない場合、行間で領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-105">If the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is not set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>, space is redistributed between rows.</span></span>  
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-106">次の条件に該当する場合は、列間で領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-106">If the following conditions are true, space is redistributed between columns:</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-107"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> に <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType> が設定されています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-107">The <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-108"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> に <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType> が設定されています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-108">The <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-109"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualWidth%2A> が <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualHeight%2A>以下の値です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-109">The <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualWidth%2A> is less than or equal to the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualHeight%2A>.</span></span>  
  
- <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-110">次の条件に該当する場合は、行の間に領域が再配分されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-110">If the following conditions are true, space is redistributed between rows:</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-111"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> は <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType> に設定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-111"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-112"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> は <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType> に設定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-112"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="ad2a4-113"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualWidth%2A> が <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualHeight%2A> より大きい値です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ad2a4-113"><xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualWidth%2A> is greater than the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualHeight%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
